{"id":9741,"date":"2023-01-16T08:58:58","date_gmt":"2023-01-16T08:58:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tblocks.com\/?p=9741"},"modified":"2023-05-19T12:27:22","modified_gmt":"2023-05-19T12:27:22","slug":"techblocks-receives-iso-27001-certification","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tblocks.com\/techblocks-receives-iso-27001-certification\/","title":{"rendered":"TechBlocks Receives ISO 27001 Certification"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>January 17, 2023 11:15 AM Eastern Standard Time<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>TORONTO&#8211;(BUSINESS WIRE)&#8211;TechBlocks, a global I.T. consulting &amp; software engineering firm has received ISO 27001 certification. ISO 27001 is an international standard to manage information security. The standard details requirements for establishing, implementing, maintaining and continually improving information security management systems (ISMS).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sabih Saddiqui, the company\u2019s CTO says, \u201cWe have always held our clients\u2019 intellectual property, data, and their clients\u2019 personally identifiable information under the strictest security protocols. Receiving ISO 27001 Certification helps reinforce the level of care we take to safeguard information we have been entrusted with.\u201d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information, the ISO 27001 certification can be viewed on the International Accreditation Forum (IAF) website&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/cts.businesswire.com\/ct\/CT?id=smartlink&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iafcertsearch.org%2Fcertification%2F0ea05d58-26c6-51d1-9bd8-4b18435d95be&amp;esheet=53214941&amp;lan=en-US&amp;anchor=here&amp;index=1&amp;md5=8aa96c5caa70a7882d7b5ba3acd6915b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>About the International Organization for Standardization (ISO)<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The International Organization for Standardization (ISO) is an independent, non-governmental, international body that develops standards to ensure the quality, safety, and efficiency of products, services, and systems. With 24,375 standards and 167 countries represented, it is a hallmark of excellence and innovation for those who carry its certification.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>About TechBlocks<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>TechBlocks\u00a0is a Canadian-based leader in IT consulting, custom software development and product engineering for companies globally. An early adopter of cloud-based Technology, TechBlocks has been serving customers in automotive, retail, utilities, telecommunications, financial services, and healthcare for over 15 years with clients that include Honda, Bell, S&amp;P Global, Bausch Health, and more. TechBlocks has offices in the USA, India, Pakistan, and Bangladesh with a global partner network of over 2,500 technology &amp; software development professionals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>For more information, please contact TechBlocks:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kevin Gordon \u2013 Director of Marketing<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>647 372 0651<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"mailto:keving@tblocks.com\">keving@tblocks.com<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>January 17, 2023 11:15 AM Eastern Standard Time TORONTO&#8211;(BUSINESS WIRE)&#8211;TechBlocks, a global I.T. consulting &amp; software engineering firm has received ISO 27001 certification. ISO 27001 is an international standard to manage information security. The standard details requirements for establishing, implementing, maintaining and continually improving information security management systems (ISMS). Sabih Saddiqui, the company\u2019s CTO says, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":9786,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"content-type":""},"categories":[26],"tb_industry":[],"tb_solution":[514],"tb_technology":[],"acf":{"tb_author":1144,"categories":26,"primary_industry":"automotive","industries":false,"primary_solution":"press-release","solutions":[514],